headline: DuPont™ Kevlar® EXO™ Named Edison Award Finalist in the Critical Safety Materials Advancement category
summary: DuPont (NYSE: DD) is proud to announce that its breakthrough innovation, Kevlar® EXO™, has been honored as a finalist for the Edison Awards(TM) in the Critical Safety Materials Advancement category.
